metadata.name: Kiki Urbano
metadata.description: Kiki knows what's getting played in all streaming services, nightclubs and parties. Latin Urban Music and Reggaeton has taken over the airwaves all over the globe. He represents our love for the hugely popular sound of latin urban, trap and Reggaeton that has taken many latin artists to crossover without having to change their language. This NFT comes with a swag bag and 2 general admission tickets to a Tickeri show of your choosing. Expires one year after purchase date. Additional exclusions may apply.
